{"tid":1355112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(總括) 我覺得依家d討論好似太散 我想試下總括下依家要做既行程 同埋有少少意見 大家可以再改再推","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T11:55:47.000Z","uid":65439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"08397e964ebde2730c7c2740932982ee711fca2a","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"其實好多post都有明確目標 但好似分得太散<br />\n手機開post唔太方便<br />\n請大家再加日期同修改<br />\n<br />\n1. 光復元朗遊行<br />\n2. 宣傳三罷 要號召時間同聯絡議員 各界<br />\n3. 宣傳追究警黑合作 721開槍鎮壓示威者<br />\n4. 繼續宣傳五大訴求<br />\n5. 大家諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n務求將同類要做既主要事 整合埋一齊 再一齊推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我最相信一句 各自爬山 永遠相信同尊重所有前線決定"},{"pid":"ab8a0f9bdb84da5cb8696ff55cb661da047efbfd","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:10:44.000Z","msg":"另外我有少少意見 關於燒村字眼，連登標題同自身立場<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n個人認為 燒村呢兩個字真係諗清楚 我覺得唔好再講 如果呢個無賴政府真係派人去燒村殺村民 到時我覺得文宣會好難搞 因為會俾人標籤屈返做恐怖份子<br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n有人連登標題其實真係睇到炆<br />\n見到d反話標題咁多正評 純睇topic既人更加唔想入去睇你d內容 因為唔知吸唔吸引到自己睇 就會搵下個post睇 你內容幾好都冇用<br />\n<br />\n3.  明確立場<br />\n你要知道對方係無賴黎 盡量唔好做一d敵人會做既野 除非你知自己做緊咩<br />\n<br />\n好似之前尖沙咀唱國歌其實我覺得有d唔知想點 d人行過咪覺得你哋愛國<br />\n<br />\n又岩岩有個國旗 post 話著上身 大家諗下會出咩問題"},{"pid":"72fb7f54b83305e1f3d4022031fb7b5aadb1a7c6","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24426c59d55148ffe2b1501e177a576989f9c13c","tid":1355112,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"圍村地圖APP<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354665\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354665</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門 share 比出嚟元朗嘅人睇"},{"pid":"afddd562788eaf9d63b572764fdd8f3d560ce498","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8584f142b5ce539aab3843de6db4b30e13bcbdd","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c5150dafeea7cf197129a88b97a4ad23c72ca64","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7271ce639078d56bd90d5af450de25f9823f4e12","tid":1355112,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"[更正] 7月26 香港國際機場集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲有機場"},{"pid":"0a8f95a4628d65b51b42f21487db9fee45ecf6ff","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:01:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c21e642121ad4701a106a903b2e1e197fe8bab6a","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9968a4031fc05cbc053b8d56184e7ec827be8c6","tid":1355112,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:14:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfbe04973511a80ee51f038c0c7795235521892f","tid":1355112,"uid":142517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"仲有追擊tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65669460c56b372fd949d48f6abe0dc09cdc0d65","tid":1355112,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"我今朝見到有個po講729三罷<br />\n而家連登係煽動爆力仇恨<br />\n三毛五毛洗版，自己友反洗版<br />\n最終搞到無晒行動策略post"},{"pid":"b7ef5c3274dccef6ad2649691fc6cb13900d67aa","tid":1355112,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65669460c56b372fd949d48f6abe0dc09cdc0d65","tid":1355112,